metadata.name: Father And Daughter
metadata.description:
All the works of this collection are physical and depicted with watercolors and colored pencils. This collection shows a symbolic world in which the fox is the symbol of women and the wolf is the symbol of men, and it can be said that it is related to a period of my life and those around me. In this work, I have mentioned the father-daughter relationship. Red flower is a symbol of affection and love. I love my dad . And I think it is one of the most beautiful relationships. I miss him everywhere I go and I want him to be the first person I talk to before doing anything.

Width 1440 pixels
Height 2000 pixels
Size: 2.2 MG
